John Law , whom the French called Jean Lass , opened a gulf into which half the nation eagerly poured its money . 
Fortunes were made in a few days in a few HOURS . 
Many were enriched by merely lending their signatures . 
A sudden and horrible revolution amazed the entire people like the bursting of a bomb shell or an incendiary explosion . 
