In vain she flattered herself that the injury she had done her husband would for ever remain one of those secrets which can only be disclosed at the last day . 
Vengeance pursued her steps , she was lost the villain to whom she had sacrificed herself boasted of the favours he had received . 
The fatal report was conveyed to her injured husband . 
He refused to believe what he thought impossible , but honour obliged him to call the boaster to the field . 
The meeting took place the profligate gambler not content with declaring , actually exulted in his guilt . 
But his triumph was of short date a bullet through the head settled his account with this world . 
But the gates of mercy were opened in vain the offender refused to receive forgiveness because she had offended . 
The lust of gambling had absorbed all her other desires . 
She gave herself up entirely to the infamous pursuit and its concomitants , whilst her husband sank by a quick decay , and died the victim of grief and anguish . 
